transformations
* aNumberOrArray 	"Answer this color with its RGB multiplied by the given number, or	multiply this color's RGB values by the corresponding entries in the	given array."	"(Color brown * 2) display"	"(Color brown * #(1 0 1)) display"	| _gsSqueakTemp_multipliers |	_gsSqueakTemp_multipliers := aNumberOrArray isCollection				ifTrue: [aNumberOrArray]				ifFalse: [Array						with: aNumberOrArray						with: aNumberOrArray						with: aNumberOrArray].	^ Color basicNew		setPrivateRed: (self privateRed * _gsSqueakTemp_multipliers first) asInteger		green: (self privateGreen * _gsSqueakTemp_multipliers second) asInteger		blue: (self privateBlue * _gsSqueakTemp_multipliers third) asInteger